    <p>Are you still relying on canes, guide dogs, confidence and spatial awareness?</p>
    <p>How terribly twentieth century.</p>
    <p>At <strong>Big Charli’s Blind Marketing Consultancy™</strong>, we asked a much more important question:</p>
    <blockquote><p>“What if navigation could involve more scalp penetration?”</p></blockquote>
    <p>Introducing <strong>The Crown of Thornes™</strong> — the world’s first AI-powered cranial guidance ecosystem.</p>
    <p>Not a mobility aid.</p>
    <p>Not a wearable.</p>
    <p>A <strong>journey enablement platform</strong>.</p>

