      <h3>Finally… Pain With Purpose™</h3>
      <p>Every gentle stab is a personalised navigation insight.</p>
      <p><strong>Wrong turn?</strong><br />Tiny spike.</p>
      <p><strong>Approaching curb?</strong><br />Several tiny spikes.</p>
      <p><strong>Busy road?</strong><br />Lots of spikes.</p>
      <p>You’re not being poked.</p>
      <p>You’re being empowered.</p>
